{"tid":997124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"絲襪癡漢出沒　見女高中生就問「妳的絲襪是幾針的」","createTime":"2019-01-27T01:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T01:57:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dc714c20c3f84d16c6dff05954e7519b2813c718","tid":997124,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:26:59.000Z","msg":"日本大阪街頭日前驚現「絲襪控」出沒，他逢女生就問「請告訴我妳的絲襪針數？」嚇壞許多女性。因附近有多所女子學校，警方研判這名絲襪控可能鎖定女高中生為目標。<br />\n <br />\n《日本集合》報導，大阪西淀川區有女性突然被騎單車的男子搭訕，男子自稱是網路名人「絲襪世界」（タイツワールド），被無視後還繼續追問「請告訴我妳的絲襪針數？」據目擊者描述，該名男子約30多歲，身高160至170公分。警方特地發出警告，呼籲西淀川區市民要小心這個男性。<br />\n <br />\n不少網友吐槽這名男子，如果真的是網紅「絲襪世界」，無法目測針數也太掉漆了吧！而「絲襪世界」本尊得知消息後，也在《推特》上po文譴責假冒他名義騷擾女性的男子。<br />\n <br />\n「絲襪世界」本尊表示，自己住在關東，這一年來都從未到訪關西。年輕時只憑肉眼就能判斷絲襪針數和品牌，現在眼睛老化了，已經失去這個技能。2015年梅田的紀伊國屋書店也曾發生「絲襪世界」騷擾女性事件，本尊推測是同一名犯人。"},{"pid":"e7f6ddca2576792dea69bd10dd752d1ed8c6d075","tid":997124,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"矮撚"},{"pid":"06bf820340501e017330e18f2365466a424c17e2","tid":997124,"uid":111271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"問野都要比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0049383eb0a37e756509b4ae904633bd04331b","tid":997124,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06bf820340501e017330e18f2365466a424c17e2","tid":997124,"uid":111271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"問野都要比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:39:08.000Z","msg":"令人不安"},{"pid":"45951bde5eca57276d1accee2a8ec209a99eaaa3","tid":997124,"uid":29627,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"10d黑絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dd95dcd9ac538711f58a18ec4b1cafc32ca7bb","tid":997124,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"最薄幾d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aec1fea042a2ff0522eaee0f8354c76e1d1f6d1","tid":997124,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"腦魔返屋企啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d2b604b1e97df803bff18eed202e7f68e303dd","tid":997124,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:57:04.000Z","msg":"「絲襪世界」（タイツワールド）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}